# Autodown Module

## Overview

Block-based Markdown editor with TipTap

## Goals

- **G1** — Block-based Markdown editor with TipTap
- **G2** — Live preview side-by-side with raw Markdown
- **G3** — Spec-aware templates and IAL table storage

